    "State-of-the-art analysis of implemented human motion intention prediction model for signal and sensor measure data.prediction techniques like ELM, CNN, LSTM, and AH-CNN-LSTM.",
    "Thus, the recommended multimodal databased human motion intention prediction framework effectively improves the accuracy of predicting human motion intentions compared to traditional mechanisms.",
    "Though the implemented model provides competitive solutions in the human motion intention prediction approach, the developed model didn't focus on class imbalance issues.",
    "This may affect the prediction performance of the developed model.",
    "Therefore, in future work, by leveraging the Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique (SMOTE) technique, the class imbalance issue will be resolved."
